# Claude API Integration with Nuvemshop

This project implements a Node.js server that integrates Claude AI with Nuvemshop's e-commerce platform to provide AI-powered support for store owners.

## Features

- REST API endpoint for chat interactions
- Integration with Anthropic's Claude AI model
- Support for Method Call Proposals (MCP) to interact with store admin functions
- Multi-language support (currently configured for pt_BR)
- Message history tracking

## Prerequisites

- Node.js
- npm
- An Anthropic API key (to be set in .env file): `ANTHROPIC_API_KEY`

